@page "/about"

<MudContainer Class="pa-0">
    <MudText Typo="Typo.h4">About D'Orc</MudText>

    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1">
        D'Orc is a free and open-source web application that provides useful tools for pen-and-paper roleplaying,
        both online and offline.<br>
        Check out the GitHub project page here: <MudLink Href="https://github.com/Phoenox/dorc" Target="_blank">github.com/Phoenox/dorc</MudLink>
    </MudText>
</MudContainer>

